"of Aviation Sans Frontières, certify that the parcel(s) covered by this "
"shipment through Aviation Sans Frontières are donation(s) from the Shipper "
"to the Recipient named below. The correspondent is the only person "
"authorized to collect these parcels on behalf of the Recipient. These "
"parcels contain only medical and surgical supplies sent for humanitarian "
"purposes. These medical items are intended for human health and are not "
"meant to be resold. They are not subject to dual-use goods rules and have no "
"commercial value. Customs value only: 1.00 euro."

