#: templates/scan/faq.html:4
msgid "WMS Scan - FAQ & Documentation"
msgstr "WMS Scan - FAQ & Documentation"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:8
msgid "Sommaire"
msgstr "Contents"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:10
msgid "Cliquez sur un titre pour aller directement à la section."
msgstr "Click a title to jump directly to the section."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:22
msgid "Vue d'ensemble"
msgstr "Overview"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:24
msgid ""
"Cette page décrit le fonctionnement complet du WMS Scan, du stock à "
"l'expédition. Les flux sont conçus pour être rapides sur mobile et pour "
"rester cohérents en base."
msgstr ""
"This page describes the full WMS Scan workflow, from stock to shipping. The "
"flows are designed to be fast on mobile and to stay consistent in the "
"database."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:31
msgid ""
"<strong>Produit</strong> : fiche article (SKU, nom, marque, poids, "
"emplacement)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Product</strong>: item sheet (SKU, name, brand, weight, location)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:32
msgid ""
"<strong>Lot</strong> : stock réel par produit (quantité, péremption, lot, "
"emplacement)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Lot</strong>: actual stock by product (quantity, expiry, lot, "
"location)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:33
msgid ""
"<strong>Carton</strong> : unité de préparation (DRAFT, PICKING, PACKED, "
"ASSIGNED, LABELED, SHIPPED)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Parcel</strong>: packing unit (DRAFT, PICKING, PACKED, ASSIGNED, "
"LABELED, SHIPPED)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:34
msgid ""
"<strong>Expédition</strong> : regroupe des cartons pour une destination."
msgstr "<strong>Shipment</strong>: groups parcels for one destination."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:35
msgid ""
"<strong>Suivi expédition</strong> : journal des scans (QR) avec horodatage."
msgstr "<strong>Shipment tracking</strong>: QR scan log with timestamps."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:37
msgid "Statuts cle"
msgstr "Key statuses"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:39
msgid ""
"<strong>Carton</strong> : Créé (draft), En préparation (picking), Prêt "
"(packed), Affecté (assigned), Étiqueté (labeled), Expédié (shipped)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Parcel</strong>: Created (draft), In preparation (picking), Ready "
"(packed), Assigned (assigned), Labeled (labeled), Shipped (shipped)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:40
msgid ""
"<strong>Expédition</strong> : Création (draft), En cours (picking), Prêt "
"(packed), Planifié (planned), Expédié (shipped), Reçu escale "
"(received_correspondent), Livré (delivered)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Shipment</strong>: Creation (draft), In progress (picking), Ready "
"(packed), Planned (planned), Shipped (shipped), Received at stopover "
"(received_correspondent), Delivered (delivered)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:41
msgid ""
"<strong>Litige</strong> : drapeau transverse sur expédition "
"(<code>is_disputed</code>), activable à tout moment du suivi."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Dispute</strong>: cross-cutting shipment flag (<code>is_disputed</"
"code>), which can be enabled at any point in tracking."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:42
msgid ""
"<strong>Réception</strong> : DRAFT tant que les lignes ne sont pas "
"réceptionnées."
msgstr "<strong>Receiving</strong>: DRAFT until the lines are received."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:47
msgid "Accès & rôles"
msgstr "Access & roles"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:49
msgid "Les pages /scan internes sont protégées par login staff."
msgstr "Internal /scan pages require staff login."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:50
msgid ""
"Le menu Compte affiche email/username, lien Admin (si staff), changer de "
"compte, déconnexion."
msgstr ""
"The Account menu shows email/username, an Admin link (for staff), switch "
"account, and logout."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:51
msgid "Imports et Templates sont réservés aux superusers."
msgstr "Imports and Templates are reserved for superusers."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:52
msgid ""
"Exception: le suivi expédition par token (/scan/shipment/track/"
"&lt;token&gt;/) est public et ne demande pas de login."
msgstr ""
"Exception: token-based shipment tracking (/scan/shipment/track/"
"&lt;token&gt;/) is public and does not require login."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:53
msgid ""
"Le suivi legacy par référence est staff-only et en consultation seule "
"(désactivable via ENABLE_SHIPMENT_TRACK_LEGACY=false)."
msgstr ""
"Legacy reference-based tracking is staff-only and read-only (can be disabled "
"via ENABLE_SHIPMENT_TRACK_LEGACY=false)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:58
msgid "Contacts (pilotage org-role)"
msgstr "Contacts (org-role control)"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:60
msgid ""
"La page <strong>Admin &gt; Contacts</strong> pilote le modèle "
"<strong>organization roles</strong> (sans CRUD legacy dans Scan)."
msgstr ""
"The <strong>Admin &gt; Contacts</strong> page controls the "
"<strong>organization roles</strong> model (without legacy CRUD in Scan)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:61
msgid ""
"Actions disponibles: activer/désactiver un rôle, gérer les contacts "
"d'organisation, lier un contact à un rôle, définir le principal."
msgstr ""
"Available actions: enable/disable a role, manage organization contacts, link "
"a contact to a role, set the primary contact."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:62
msgid "Périmètre expéditeur: scopes globaux ou par destination."
msgstr "Shipper scope: global scopes or per-destination scopes."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:63
msgid "Périmètre destinataire: bindings expéditeur + destination."
msgstr "Recipient scope: shipper + destination bindings."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:64
msgid ""
"Onboarding guidé: création d'une organisation + rôle + contact principal "
"depuis le cockpit."
msgstr ""
"Guided onboarding: create an organization + role + primary contact from the "
"cockpit."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:65
msgid ""
"Les liens admin Django restent disponibles en secours pour les opérations de "
"maintenance."
msgstr ""
"Django admin links remain available as a fallback for maintenance operations."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:70
msgid "Données de référence"
msgstr "Reference data"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:71
msgid "Avant utilisation, vérifier ces données :"
msgstr "Before use, verify the following data:"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:73
msgid "<strong>Organisations</strong> actives (type Organisation)."
msgstr "<strong>Organizations</strong> active (Organization type)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:74
msgid ""
"<strong>Rôles actifs</strong> selon le besoin métier (expéditeur, "
"destinataire, correspondant, donateur, transporteur)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Active roles</strong> according to business need (shipper, "
"recipient, correspondent, donor, carrier)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:75
msgid ""
"Pour un rôle actif: un <strong>contact principal actif avec email</strong> "
"doit être lié."
msgstr ""
"For an active role, an <strong>active primary contact with email</strong> "
"must be linked."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:76
msgid ""
"Pour les expéditeurs: définir les <strong>scopes</strong> (global ou "
"destination)."
msgstr ""
"For shippers: define the <strong>scopes</strong> (global or destination-"
"specific)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:77
msgid ""
"Pour les destinataires: définir les <strong>bindings</strong> avec les "
"expéditeurs et destinations autorisés."
msgstr ""
"For recipients: define the <strong>bindings</strong> with authorized "
"shippers and destinations."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:78
msgid ""
"<strong>Destinations</strong> : ville, code IATA, pays, correspondant lié."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Destinations</strong>: city, IATA code, country, linked "
"correspondent."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:79
msgid ""
"<strong>Formats de carton</strong> : un format par défaut pour la "
"préparation."
msgstr "<strong>Parcel formats</strong>: one default format for preparation."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:80
msgid ""
"<strong>Entrepôts</strong> et <strong>Emplacements</strong> : entrepôt / "
"rack / étagère / bac."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Warehouses</strong> and <strong>Locations</strong>: warehouse / "
"rack / shelf / bin."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:81
msgid "<strong>Couleurs rack</strong> : associées à un rack (entrepôt + zone)."
msgstr "<strong>Rack colors</strong>: attached to a rack (warehouse + zone)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:82
msgid ""
"<strong>Catégories</strong> : hiérarchie L1 -> L4 (créées à l'import si "
"besoin)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Categories</strong>: L1 -> L4 hierarchy (created during import if "
"needed)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:85
msgid "Quand un sélecteur n'a qu'un seul choix, il est auto-sélectionné."
msgstr "When a selector has only one choice, it is auto-selected."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:92
msgid "Recherche multi-clés : nom, SKU, barcode, EAN."
msgstr "Multi-key search: name, SKU, barcode, EAN."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:93
msgid "Filtres : catégorie, entrepôt. Tri : catégorie, nom, référence, stock."
msgstr "Filters: category, warehouse. Sort: category, name, reference, stock."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:94
msgid ""
"Le switch <strong>Inclure les produits avec stock à 0</strong> permet "
"d'afficher aussi les produits sans stock disponible."
msgstr ""
"The <strong>Include products with 0 stock</strong> switch also displays "
"products without available stock."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:95
msgid "Le stock affiché correspond aux lots disponibles."
msgstr "Displayed stock matches the available lots."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:96
msgid ""
"La colonne <strong>Dernière modification</strong> suit les mouvements de "
"stock."
msgstr "The <strong>Last modified</strong> column follows stock movements."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:97
msgid ""
"Dans les pages <strong>Vue...</strong>, chaque en-tête de colonne est "
"triable et filtrable."
msgstr ""
"On <strong>View...</strong> pages, each column header can be sorted and "
"filtered."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:104
msgid "Sélection produit par nom, SKU, barcode ou EAN (scan caméra possible)."
msgstr ""
"Select a product by name, SKU, barcode, or EAN (camera scan supported)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:105
msgid "Si inconnu, le bouton propose de créer le produit dans l'admin."
msgstr "If unknown, the button offers to create the product in the admin."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:106
msgid "Quantité, péremption et lot sont enregistrés dans un nouveau lot."
msgstr "Quantity, expiry date, and lot are saved in a new lot."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:107
msgid "Le lot est placé sur l'emplacement par défaut du produit."
msgstr "The lot is placed in the product's default location."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:108
msgid ""
"Les champs Marque / Emplacement / Entrepôt s'affichent en lecture seule."
msgstr "Brand / Location / Warehouse fields are displayed read-only."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:115
msgid "Retire du stock pour casse, perte ou correction."
msgstr "Removes stock for breakage, loss, or correction."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:116
msgid "Référence expédition optionnelle pour tracer un flux."
msgstr "Optional shipment reference to trace a flow."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:117
msgid "Motif + notes permettent de justifier la sortie."
msgstr "Reason + notes make it possible to justify the stock removal."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:122
msgid "Préparation (cartons)"
msgstr "Preparation (parcels)"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:124
msgid "Choisir un format de carton (ou personnaliser les dimensions)."
msgstr "Choose a parcel format (or customize the dimensions)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:125
msgid "Ajouter une ou plusieurs lignes produit + quantité (scan possible)."
msgstr "Add one or more product + quantity lines (scanning supported)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:126
msgid ""
"Le système peut créer plusieurs cartons selon la capacité (poids/volume)."
msgstr ""
"The system can create several parcels based on capacity (weight/volume)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:127
msgid ""
"Si un produit n'a pas de dimensions/poids, activez le switch d'autorisation "
"pour appliquer les valeurs standard (1 x 1 x 1 cm et 5 g)."
msgstr ""
"If a product has no dimensions/weight, enable the override switch to apply "
"standard values (1 x 1 x 1 cm and 5 g)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:128
msgid "Optionnel : référence expédition pour affecter directement les cartons."
msgstr "Optional: shipment reference to assign parcels directly."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:129
msgid "Optionnel : emplacement courant pour tracer le stockage temporaire."
msgstr "Optional: current location to trace temporary storage."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:132
msgid ""
"Un carton assigné à une expédition affiche le statut <strong>Affecté</"
"strong> dans la Vue Colis."
msgstr ""
"A parcel assigned to a shipment shows the <strong>Assigned</strong> status "
"in Parcel view."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:138
msgid ""
"Le code carton suit le format <strong>TYPE-AAAAMMJJ-N</strong> (type "
"dominant par poids). Le volume est calculé avec les dimensions du carton "
"(format par défaut si non renseigné)."
msgstr ""
"The parcel code follows the <strong>TYPE-YYYYMMDD-N</strong> format "
"(dominant type by weight). Volume is calculated from the parcel dimensions "
"(default format if not provided)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:146 templates/scan/shipment_create.html:14
#: wms/admin.py:771
msgid "Créer une expédition"
msgstr "Create shipment"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:148
msgid ""
"Séquencement: destination d'abord, puis expéditeur, puis destinataire + "
"correspondant, puis le reste du formulaire."
msgstr ""
"Sequence: destination first, then shipper, then recipient + correspondent, "
"then the rest of the form."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:149
msgid ""
"Expéditeur: tag <strong>Expéditeur</strong> + destination explicite ou "
"globale (destinations vides)."
msgstr ""
"Shipper: <strong>Shipper</strong> tag + explicit or global destination "
"(empty destinations)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:150
msgid ""
"Destinataire: tag <strong>Destinataire</strong> + expéditeur lié explicite "
"ou global (expéditeurs liés vides)."
msgstr ""
"Recipient: <strong>Recipient</strong> tag + explicit or global linked "
"shipper (empty linked shippers)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:151
msgid ""
"Correspondant: tag <strong>Correspondant</strong> + destination; si la "
"destination a un correspondant lié, ce choix est imposé."
msgstr ""
"Correspondent: <strong>Correspondent</strong> tag + destination; if the "
"destination has a linked correspondent, that choice is enforced."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:152
msgid ""
"Si aucun correspondant n'est lié à la destination, le sélecteur "
"correspondant reste vide."
msgstr ""
"If no correspondent is linked to the destination, the correspondent selector "
"stays empty."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:153
msgid ""
"Ajouter des cartons <strong>Prêt</strong> non affectés, ou créer des cartons "
"depuis des produits."
msgstr ""
"Add unassigned <strong>Ready</strong> parcels, or create parcels from "
"products."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:154
msgid ""
"À l'affectation à l'expédition, un carton passe en statut <strong>Affecté</"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"When assigned to the shipment, a parcel moves to the <strong>Assigned</"
"strong> status."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:155
msgid ""
"<strong>Enregistrer en brouillon</strong> crée une expédition temporaire "
"<strong>EXP-TEMP-XX</strong> modifiable plus tard."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Save draft</strong> creates a temporary shipment <strong>EXP-TEMP-"
"XX</strong> that can be edited later."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:156
msgid ""
"<strong>Créer des colis multi-produits</strong> (depuis la création) "
"enregistre d'abord un brouillon puis ouvre l'onglet Préparation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Create multi-product parcels</strong> (from creation) first saves a "
"draft, then opens the Preparation tab."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:157
msgid "Le poids total est calculé automatiquement."
msgstr "Total weight is calculated automatically."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:158
msgid "En modification: QR, documents, étiquettes et uploads additionnels."
msgstr "When editing: QR, documents, labels, and additional uploads."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:165
msgid "Liste tous les cartons préparés avec leur statut et contenu."
msgstr "Lists all prepared parcels with their status and contents."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:166
msgid ""
"Actions explicites: <strong>Marquer étiqueté</strong> et <strong>Retirer "
"étiquette</strong> pour les cartons affectés."
msgstr ""
"Explicit actions: <strong>Mark labeled</strong> and <strong>Remove label</"
"strong> for assigned parcels."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:167
msgid ""
"Un carton affecté/étiqueté désaffecté d'une expédition revient en "
"<strong>Prêt</strong>."
msgstr ""
"An assigned/labeled parcel that is removed from a shipment goes back to "
"<strong>Ready</strong>."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:168
msgid "Un carton <strong>Expédié</strong> n'est plus modifiable."
msgstr "A <strong>Shipped</strong> parcel can no longer be edited."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:169
msgid ""
"Poids et remplissage sont affichés quand les dimensions sont disponibles."
msgstr "Weight and fill level are displayed when dimensions are available."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:176
msgid ""
"<strong>Brouillon</strong> : expédition temporaire (référence <strong>EXP-"
"TEMP-XX</strong>) sauvegardée pour reprise ultérieure."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Draft</strong>: temporary shipment (reference <strong>EXP-TEMP-XX</"
"strong>) saved for later completion."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:177
msgid ""
"<strong>Création</strong> : expédition active sans colis étiqueté (référence "
"finale)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Creation</strong>: active shipment without labeled parcels (final "
"reference)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:178
msgid ""
"<strong>En cours</strong> : tant que tous les colis ne sont pas étiquetés."
msgstr "<strong>In progress</strong>: until all parcels are labeled."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:179
msgid "<strong>Prêt</strong> : tous les colis sont étiquetés."
msgstr "<strong>Ready</strong>: all parcels are labeled."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:180
msgid ""
"<strong>Planifié</strong> : verrouille la modification des colis de "
"l'expédition."
msgstr "<strong>Planned</strong>: locks editing of the shipment's parcels."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:181
msgid ""
"<strong>Expédié</strong>, <strong>Reçu escale</strong>, <strong>Livré</"
"strong> : progression via le suivi."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Shipped</strong>, <strong>Received at stopover</strong>, "
"<strong>Delivered</strong>: progression through tracking."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:182
msgid ""
"<strong>Litige</strong> : préfixe visuel sur le statut (ex: \"Litige - "
"Planifié\")."
msgstr ""
