msgid ""
"Utilisateurs: mot de passe obligatoire si IMPORT_DEFAULT_PASSWORD est vide."
msgstr "Users: password required if IMPORT_DEFAULT_PASSWORD is empty."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:303
msgid "Templates (admin)"
msgstr "Templates (admin)"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:305
msgid ""
"La page <strong>Gestion &gt; Templates</strong> pilote les templates XLSX "
"Print Pack (superuser uniquement)."
msgstr ""
"The <strong>Management &gt; Templates</strong> page controls XLSX Print Pack "
"templates (superuser only)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:306
msgid ""
"Chaque ligne correspond à un document: <strong>pack + doc_type + variant</"
"strong>."
msgstr ""
"Each row corresponds to one document: <strong>pack + doc_type + variant</"
"strong>."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:307
msgid ""
"Vous pouvez uploader/remplacer le fichier <strong>.xlsx</strong> actif du "
"document."
msgstr ""
"You can upload/replace the active document <strong>.xlsx</strong> file."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:308
msgid ""
"Le mapping se fait par ligne, avec listes déroulantes: <strong>worksheet</"
"strong>, <strong>colonne</strong>, <strong>ligne</strong>, <strong>champ "
"source</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Mapping is defined row by row, with dropdowns for <strong>worksheet</"
"strong>, <strong>column</strong>, <strong>row</strong>, and <strong>source "
"field</strong>."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:309
msgid ""
"Les champs source sont limités à un catalogue backend (pas de saisie "
"manuelle libre)."
msgstr "Source fields are limited to a backend catalog (no free manual entry)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:310
msgid "Plusieurs changements peuvent être enregistrés en une seule sauvegarde."
msgstr "Several changes can be saved in one submission."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:311
msgid ""
"Si une cellule est fusionnée, le mapping est normalisé automatiquement sur "
"la cellule d'ancrage."
msgstr ""
"If a cell is merged, the mapping is automatically normalized to the anchor "
"cell."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:312
msgid ""
"Chaque sauvegarde crée une version (snapshot fichier + mappings) avec "
"restauration possible depuis l'historique."
msgstr ""
"Each save creates a version (file snapshot + mappings) that can be restored "
"from history."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:313
msgid ""
"En cas de rollback, restaurer une version applique le fichier XLSX et les "
"mappings associés."
msgstr ""
"In case of rollback, restoring a version applies the XLSX file and its "
"associated mappings."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:318
msgid "Suivi expédition (QR)"
msgstr "Shipment tracking (QR)"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:320
msgid "Un QR code est généré à la création de l'expédition."
msgstr "A QR code is generated when the shipment is created."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:321
msgid "Le scan ouvre une page publique avec documents + historique."
msgstr "Scanning it opens a public page with documents + history."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:322
msgid ""
"Champs obligatoires : <strong>Nom</strong> et <strong>Structure</strong>."
msgstr "Required fields: <strong>Name</strong> and <strong>Structure</strong>."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:323
msgid "Commentaires optionnels et horodatage automatique (AAAA/MM/JJ HHhMM)."
msgstr "Optional comments and automatic timestamp (YYYY/MM/DD HHhMM)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:324
msgid "Le sélecteur propose automatiquement l'étape suivante."
msgstr "The selector automatically proposes the next step."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:325
msgid ""
"Étapes : OK pour planification, Planifié, Déplacé au magasin export, OK mise "
"à bord, Reçu correspondant, Reçu destinataire."
msgstr ""
"Steps: OK for planning, Planned, Moved to export warehouse, Boarding OK, "
"Received by correspondent, Received by recipient."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:326
msgid ""
"Passage de statut expédition : Planifié/Déplacé => Planifié, Mise à bord => "
"Expédié, Reçu correspondant => Reçu escale, Reçu destinataire => Livré."
msgstr ""
"Shipment status transition: Planned/Moved => Planned, Boarding => Shipped, "
"Received by correspondent => Received at stopover, Received by recipient => "
"Delivered."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:327
msgid ""
"Depuis la page de suivi staff, le bouton <strong>Revenir à la liste</strong> "
"revient vers la dernière vue (Vue Expéditions ou Suivi des expéditions)."
msgstr ""
"From the staff tracking page, the <strong>Back to list</strong> button "
"returns to the last view (Shipments view or Shipment tracking)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:328
msgid ""
"Si des champs de suivi sont modifiés non enregistrés, une confirmation "
"propose <strong>OUI</strong> (enregistrer) ou <strong>NON</strong> (quitter "
"sans enregistrer)."
msgstr ""
"If unsaved tracking fields have been modified, a confirmation offers "
"<strong>YES</strong> (save) or <strong>NO</strong> (leave without saving)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:329
msgid ""
"Depuis le suivi, vous pouvez <strong>Déclarer litige</strong> puis "
"<strong>Résoudre litige et remettre Prêt</strong>."
msgstr ""
"From tracking, you can <strong>Declare dispute</strong> then <strong>Resolve "
"dispute and reset to Ready</strong>."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:332
msgid ""
"Pour que le QR fonctionne depuis un téléphone, définir "
"<strong>SITE_BASE_URL</strong> sur l'environnement de déploiement."
msgstr ""
"For the QR code to work from a phone, set <strong>SITE_BASE_URL</strong> in "
"the deployment environment."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:340
msgid "Scanner & synchronisation"
msgstr "Scanner & sync"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:342
msgid ""
"Le bouton <strong>Scan</strong> ouvre la caméra et remplit le champ cible."
msgstr ""
"The <strong>Scan</strong> button opens the camera and fills the target field."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:343
msgid "Si la caméra est bloquée, autoriser l'accès dans le navigateur."
msgstr "If the camera is blocked, allow access in the browser."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:344
msgid "Si le scan n'est pas supporté, saisir le code manuellement."
msgstr "If scanning is not supported, enter the code manually."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:345
msgid ""
"Le QR expédition ouvre uniquement la page de suivi + documents (sans login)."
msgstr "The shipment QR opens only the tracking + documents page (no login)."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:346
msgid "La bannière de synchro indique qu'une mise à jour est disponible."
msgstr "The sync banner indicates that an update is available."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:351
msgid "FAQ rapide"
msgstr "Quick FAQ"

#: templates/scan/faq.html:353
msgid ""
"<strong>Mes listes sont vides</strong> : vérifier les rôles actifs, scopes "
"expéditeurs et bindings destinataires."
msgstr ""
"<strong>My lists are empty</strong>: check active roles, shipper scopes, and "
"recipient bindings."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:354
msgid ""
"<strong>Je ne vois plus \"créer / modifier / supprimer contact\" dans Scan</"
"strong> : c'est normal, le CRUD legacy a été retiré au profit du cockpit org-"
"role."
msgstr ""
"<strong>I no longer see \"create / edit / delete contact\" in Scan</strong>: "
"this is expected, the legacy CRUD was removed in favor of the org-role "
"cockpit."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:355
msgid ""
"<strong>Stock à zéro</strong> : vérifier les lots disponibles et leur "
"emplacement."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Zero stock</strong>: check the available lots and their location."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:356
msgid ""
"<strong>Caméra ne s'ouvre pas</strong> : autoriser la caméra, tester un "
"autre navigateur."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Camera does not open</strong>: allow camera access, try another "
"browser."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:357
msgid ""
"<strong>Un carton est bloqué</strong> : un carton expédié est non "
"modifiable, et une expédition planifiée/verrouillée bloque les changements "
"colis."
msgstr ""
"<strong>A parcel is blocked</strong>: a shipped parcel cannot be edited, and "
"a planned/locked shipment blocks parcel changes."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:358
msgid ""
"<strong>Correspondant introuvable</strong> : vérifier le correspondant lié "
"sur la destination sélectionnée."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Correspondent not found</strong>: check the correspondent linked to "
"the selected destination."

#: templates/scan/faq.html:359
msgid ""
"<strong>Le QR n'ouvre rien</strong> : vérifier SITE_BASE_URL et relancer "
"l'app."
msgstr ""
"<strong>The QR code opens nothing</strong>: check SITE_BASE_URL and restart "
"the app."

